platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Here’s how it starts: Spin a few switches, and your wandering adventurers can reach their destination. Simple enough. But then add time loops, characters bumping into each other, locked areas, and the inescapable tentacles of submerged monsters. Not so easy now, right? Thankfully gorgeous art, atmospheric audio, and rewarding challenges make this time-bender wonderfully timeless.
